message.raw:
@{557058:90bc87b0-2886-4377-a17c-3a6629a697ff}  pointed out this:

* The recorded log was looking for version 4 of the fuel model, but he had version 5.
* ign fuel download is not downloading to the correct location according to the version argument -v 4
message.html:
@Addisu Z. Taddese pointed out this:

  • The recorded log was looking for version 4 of the fuel model, but he had version 5.
  • ign fuel download is not downloading to the correct location according to the version argument -v 4
